{"id":"7732","name":"bright-early-bieber-fever-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Bieber Fever Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2011-09-29T09:30:00-05:00","tags":[],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/amyallmandfoto/6174050574/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6167/6174050574_5d30fefc9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. Your tour of this morning&#x2019;s headlines:</p><ul><li>So Justin Bieber was in town yesterday filming some sort of Christmas video in Franklin Square involving a snow machine and everyone freaked out! We, however, remained perfectly calm. <em>Perfectly calm</em>. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20110928/WILLIAMSON01/309280141/Justin-Bieber-draws-crowds-downtown-Franklin-video\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>The Tennessee Highway Patrol reports that they&#x2019;ve made 39% more drunk driving arrests this year than in past years. So far they&#x2019;ve picked up nearly 3,500 folks for getting behind the wheel impaired. [<a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/2e642ff0-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WZTV</a>]</li><li>A cross-dressing male was attacked in West Nashville last night, making him the second cross-dressing victim of an assault this week. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/15567442/man-dressed-as-woman-attacked-in-west-nashville\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>It may be getting a little warm today, but expect things to get pretty darn fall-ish after tonight. [<a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2011/09/warm-afternoon-then-big-changes/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville WX</a>]</li><li>In the latest installment of new Sounds stadium rumors, one property owner would like to put it right by LP Field near that nasty scrap metal place on the river. [<a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/pitch-made-sounds-stadium-east-banks-north-end?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+NashvilleCityPaper-CityNews+%28Nashville+City+Paper+-+City+News%29&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">City Paper</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/amyallmandfoto/6174050574/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Amy Allmand</a>.</em></p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}